# 📄 Visual Studio and C++ project ignores
# These rules prevent temporary build files, IDE-specific configs, 
# and user-specific settings from cluttering version control.

# 🔧 IDE folders
.vs/                      # Visual Studio workspace settings
*.suo                     # Solution user options
*.user                    # User-specific project settings

# 🧠 IntelliSense & cache
*.VC.db                   # IntelliSense database
*.VC.opendb               # IntelliSense session data
*.ipch/                   # Precompiled header cache
*.ncb                     # IntelliSense (legacy)
*.sdf                     # SQL Server Compact database
*.cache/                  # Build cache files

# 🛠️ Build artifacts
*.obj                     # Object files from compilation
*.exe                     # Compiled binaries
*.pdb                     # Program database (debug info)
*.ilk                     # Incremental linker file
*.idb                     # Debug symbol database
*.aps                     # Binary resource file

# 🧪 Build output folders
Debug/
Release/
x64/
x86/
*.tlog/                  # Compiler log files

# 📜 Logs
*.log                    # General logs (optional: scope to build logs)